  Guidance on nationality and eligibility for applicants.
*/
---
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Nationality Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    Applicants must have the right to work in the UK. This includes:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
    <li>UK nationals</li>
    <li>Nationals of the Republic of Ireland</li>
    <li>Nationals of Commonwealth countries with the right to work in the UK</li>
    <li>Nationals of the EU, Switzerland, Norway, Iceland, or Liechtenstein with settled or pre-settled status under the EU Settlement Scheme</li>
    <li>Individuals with limited leave to remain or indefinite leave to remain who were eligible to apply for EU Settlement Scheme before 31 December 2020</li>
  </ul>